1. d4 ({Following this repertoire, the more common move-order is} 1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 c5 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 g6 5. Nc3 Bg7 6. e4 d6 7. Be2 Nc6 8. Be3 O-O 9. O-O Bd7 10. h3) 1... Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. e4 O-O 5. h3 c5 6. Nf3 cxd4 7. Nxd4 Nc6 8. Be3 d6 9. Be2 Bd7 10. O-O Nxd4 11. Bxd4 Bc6 12. Qc2 a5 13. Rad1 Nd7 14. Bxg7 Kxg7 15. Bg4 $1 Ne5 (15... Nc5 16. e5 $16) (15... h5 16. Bxd7 Qxd7 17. c5 $16 (17. e5 $16)) 16. c5 Nxg4 17. hxg4 Qd7 18. cxd6 exd6 19. f3 $16 Rac8 20. Qf2 $1 Qe6 (20... Rfd8 21. Qd4+ (21. Nd5 $2 {is a strategic mistake: The knight is clearly superior to the bishop and should be preserved.} Bxd5 22. Rxd5 $14) 21... Kg8 22. Rd2 b5 23. Rfd1 b4 24. Ne2 $16) 21. Qd4+ Kg8 22. Qxd6 Qc4 23. Qd4 Qe6 24. Kf2 Rfd8 25. Qb6 Re8 26. Rd2 a4 27. a3 Qf6 28. Rfd1 h5 29. gxh5 Qh4+ 30. Kg1 Qxh5 31. Rd8 Qg5 32. Rxc8 Rxc8 33. Qd4 Re8 34. Qd2 Qc5+ 35. Qf2 Qg5 36. g3 f5 37. Nd5 fxe4 38. fxe4 Bxd5 39. exd5 Re3 40. d6 Rxg3+ 41. Kf1 Qg4 42. Rd4 Qh3+ 43. Ke1 Qh1+ 44. Ke2 Rg2 45. d7 Rxf2+ 46. Kxf2 Qh2+ 47. Ke3 Qg3+ 48. Ke2 Qg2+ 49. Kd3 Qf3+ 50. Kd2 Qf2+ 51. Kd3 Qg3+ 52. Ke2 Qh2+ 53. Kd3 Qh3+ 54. Kd2 Qh2+ 55. Kd3 Qh3+ 56. Kd2 Qg2+ 57. Kd3 Qf3+ 58. Kd2 Qf2+ 59. Kd3 Qf5+ 60. Kc3 Qa5+ 61. Kd3 Qd8 62. Ke4 Kf7 63. Ke5 Ke7 64. Rd6 Qh8+ 65. Kd5 Qh5+ 66. Kc4 Kd8 67. Rd4 b5+ 68. Kb4 g5 69. Kxb5 g4+ 70. Kc6 g3 71. Re4 Qf3 72. Kd6 Qxe4 0-1

