1. Nf3 Nf6 2. g3 b6 3. Bg2 Bb7 4. O-O g6 5. c4 c5 6. b3 Bg7 7. Bb2 O-O 8. Nc3 d5 9. Nxd5 Nxd5 10. Bxg7 Kxg7 11. cxd5 Qxd5 12. d4 cxd4 13. Qxd4+ Qxd4 14. Nxd4 Bxg2 15. Kxg2 Na6 16. Rac1 Rfd8 17. Rfd1 Rac8 18. Rxc8 Rxc8 19. Nb5 Rc2 20. a3 Rxe2 21. b4 Re5 22. Nxa7 Nc7 23. Rd7 Nd5 24. Nc6 Re6 25. Nd4 Re5 26. f4 Nf6 27. fxe5 Nxd7 28. Nc6 f5 29. exf6+ Kxf6 30. a4 e5 31. a5 bxa5 32. bxa5 {White created a distant passed pawn} Ke6 33. a6 Kd6 34. a7 Nb6 35. Na5 Kd5 (35... Kc7 36. Nc4 $1 $18) 36. Kf3 Na8 37. Ke3 Nc7 38. g4 Na8 39. h4 Nc7 40. g5 Na8 41. Nb3 Nc7 42. Nd2 Na8 43. Ne4 Ke6 44. Kf3 Nc7 45. Nf2 Kf5 46. Ne4 Na8 47. Ng3+ Ke6 48. Ke4 Nc7 49. Nf1 Kd6 50. Ne3 Kc6 51. Nc4 Kb7 52. Kxe5 Kxa7 53. Nd2 Kb6 54. Ne4 Kc6 55. Nf6 Nb5 56. Nxh7 Nd6 57. Nf8 Nf7+ 58. Kf6 Nd6 59. Nxg6 1-0

