1. c4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. b3 d6 4. Bb2 e5 5. g3 Bg7 6. Bg2 O-O 7. O-O c5 8. d3 Nc6 9. Nc3 h6 (9... Be6 10. Ng5 Bd7 (10... Qd7 11. Nxe6 $16) 11. a3 h6 (11... Rb8 12. b4 $1 (12. Rb1 {is also playable})) 12. Nge4 Nxe4 13. dxe4 $5 Be6 14. e3 $14) (9... Re8 10. a3 e4 $6 (10... h6 11. Nd2 Be6 12. Nd5 Bxd5 $2 13. cxd5 Ne7 14. e4 Nd7 15. Nc4 $1 (15. b4 $16) (15. f4 $16) 15... Qc7 16. a4 a6 17. a5 b5 18. axb6 Nxb6 19. Na5 $16) (10... Be6 11. Ng5 Bd7 12. Rb1 $1 Rb8 (12... a6 13. b4 $14) 13. Bc1 $1 $14 {Incredible move! Only in the system c5-d6-e5} (13. e3 {is also possible}) 13... a6 (13... h6 14. Nge4 Nxe4 15. dxe4 $16) 14. b4 cxb4 15. axb4 b5 16. Nge4 $14) 11. dxe4 Nxe4 12. Nxe4 Rxe4 (12... Bxb2 13. Ra2 Bg7 $2 14. Nxd6 $18) 13. Ng5 $1 $16 (13. Bxg7 Kxg7 14. Ra2 $1 $16 {[%cal Ga1a2,Ga2d2]}) 13... Re7 14. Bxg7 Kxg7 15. Ra2 $1 $16 (15. Ne4 Bh3 16. Nc3 Bxg2 17. Kxg2 $16)) 10. a3 $1 {[%cal Gf3d2]} (10. Nd2 Be6 11. Nd5 $2 (11. a3 $1) 11... Bxd5 12. cxd5 Nb4 $1 $13) 10... Be6 (10... Re8 11. Nd2 Be6 12. Nd5) 11. b4 $5 {This is also playable and good enough for a small advantage} (11. Nd2 $1 d5 $6 {The concrete variation that we need to know - take on d5 and Rc1! If Black takes Nxc3 after that, Rxc3!} (11... Rc8 12. Nd5 Bxd5 13. cxd5 Ne7 14. e4 Nd7 {White has several good moves in this position} 15. b4 $16 (15. a4 $16) (15. f4 $16) (15. Nc4 Qc7 16. a4 f5 17. f4 exf4 18. Bxg7 Kxg7 19. gxf4 $16)) (11... Rb8 12. Nd5 Ne7 13. Nxf6+ $1 Bxf6 14. b4 b6 15. Bc3 (15. Ne4 Bg7 16. Nc3 $14) 15... Bg7 16. a4 f5 17. a5 g5 18. axb6 axb6 19. Ra7 $16) 12. cxd5 Nxd5 13. Rc1 $1 $16) 11... cxb4 12. axb4 Nxb4 13. Ba3 a5 14. Rb1 d5 15. Bxb4 axb4 16. Rxb4 dxc4 17. dxc4 Qa5 18. Qb3 Nd7 19. Rb5 Qa3 20. Qxa3 Rxa3 21. Nd5 Ra2 22. e3 Rc2 23. Rxb7 Rxc4 24. Nd2 Rc2 25. Ne4 Bxd5 26. Rxd7 Be6 27. Rd6 Rb8 28. h4 Bf8 29. Rxe6 fxe6 30. Rd1 Rc7 31. Ra1 Kf7 32. Ra5 Rd8 33. Bh3 (33. Rxe5 Rd5) 33... Bg7 34. Ra6 Re7 35. Nd6+ Kf8 36. Kg2 Rb8 37. Ne4 Kg8 38. Bxe6+ Kh7 39. Bd5 Rd7 40. Be6 Rc7 41. Nd6 Rf8 42. Ne4 Rb8 43. g4 Rb4 44. h5 gxh5 (44... Rxe4 45. hxg6+ Kh8 46. Ra8+ Bf8 47. Rxf8+ Kg7 48. Rg8+ Kf6 49. Bf5 $14) 45. Bf5+ Kg8 46. gxh5 Kf7 47. Bg6+ Ke7 48. Ng3 Kd7 49. Nf5 Kc8 50. Ra8+ Kb7 51. Rg8 Bf6 52. Nxh6 Rh4 53. Nf5 Rg4+ 54. Kf3 Rg5 55. Nd6+ Kc6 56. Ne4 1-0

